divs: sighting detailsit was 8:35 - 9:00 my mom and dad were playing tennis and i was staring at the sky and i stood on the side of the tennis court when i was bored and i saw a strange flying object. it fly as fast as a helicopter so it couldn't be a standard like, heathrow aeroplane . it had a bright (sort of uv) orange color ,and the main color was grey\black . the trees at the location were about 4.5 metres tall so the ufo from the human eye seemed about 6-7 metres off the ground. i lost sight of the ufo when it hid behind a group of trees and somehow it vanished. i felt as though i had seen a miracle and i couldn't belive my eyes!
